	* menus/makefile.msc : build menus with nmake, too
	* menus/Makefile.am : added to EXTRA_DIST

	* **/makefile.msc app/gimpcore.def : updated

	* app/base/temp-buf.c : there is no pid_t with msvc so typedef one

